ies\n|Adelaide Kane\n|{{nominated}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n|[[People's Choice Awards]]\n|Favorite New TV Drama\n|''Reign''\n|{{won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite news |author=<!-- Staff report --> |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/people/2014/01/08/peoples-choice-awards-2014-winners-list/4380307/ |title=People's Choice Awards 2014: The winners |work=[[USA Today]] |date=January 9, 2014 |accessdate=September 13, 2016}}</ref>\n\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|2015\n|Golden Maple Awards\n|Best Actor in a TV series broadcast in US\n|Torrance Coombs & Jonathan Keltz\n|{{nominated}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/golden-maple-awards-nominees-revealed-791918|title=2015 GOLDEN MAPLE AWARDS Nomintations|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=April 28, 2015|accessdate=September 13, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Canadian Screen Awards]]\n|Best Achievement in Make-Up\n|\"Consummation\"<br />Jenny Arbour, Linda Preston\n|{{nominated}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"Canada Screen 2015\">{{cite news|url=http://www.academy.ca/getmedia/eebf59d3-3966-4172-973d-ca194be6c13e/2015_CSA_-Television_-Nominations.aspx?ext=.pdf |title=2015 CANADIAN SCREEN AWARDS Television Nominations |publisher=Academy of Canadian Cinema & Television |accessdate=January 20, 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115095449/http://www.academy.ca/getmedia/eebf59d3-3966-4172-973d-ca194be6c13e/2015_CSA_-Television_-Nominations.aspx?ext=.pdf |archivedate=January 15, 2015 }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Canadian Screen Awards]]\n|Shaw Media Award for Best Performance by an Actress in a Continuing Leading Dramatic Role\n|Megan Follows\n|{{nominated}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"Canada Screen 2015\" />\n\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2016\n|[[Canadian Screen Awards]]\n|Best Production Design or Art Direction in a Fiction Program or Series\n|\"Acts of War\"<br />Phillip Barker, Robert Hepburn, Brad Milburn\n|